data.description: Beautiful home in Monticello Ranch neighborhood, close to major highways, shopping and easy commute to Lackland AFB. Spacious 3 BR, 2.5 Bath two stories stone/brick elevation. This home has a large family room, eat in kitchen with a breakfast bar. All three bedrooms with an especially large master are upstairs with nice size loft. There is an ample sized backyard, sprinkler system with cove patio. See floor plan in the Documents Section.
